6 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to authorize the
7 Governor during a declared state of emergency to authorize the Agency of
8 Natural Resources to waive applicable water quality permits or requirements to
9 allow dams within the State to draw down water levels in anticipation of a
10 flood event likely to cause substantial damage or injury to persons or property.
